Introduction
Welcome to the services of Mageeks Apps & Games, brand of Consulit s.c. and it’s affiliates (“Mageeks”, “we”, “us”, “our”) located in Warsaw, Poland. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy applies to Mageeks’s products, mobile applications, services and websites including
www.mageeks.com
,
www.constructionsimulatorpro.com,
eurotruckpro.com
,
trainsimulatorpro.com
and any of its subdomains (the “Sites”), and any Mageeks application (“Game”) provided on a mobile platform (for example Android, iOS, Amazon). Personal information is information about you that is personally identifiable like your name or email address and that is not otherwise publicly available.
By using the Service, you are expressing your agreement to this Policy and the processing of your data, including your personal information, in the manner provided in this Policy. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Service.
This policy does not apply to the practices of companies that Megeeks does not own or control or to people that Megeeks does not employ or manage. Privacy Policy applies to personal data that we process when you use the Service. It does not apply to any links to third parties’ websites and/or services, such as third-party applications or websites of any advertisers, payment providers, rewards program providers or any other third parties which you may encounter when you use the Service. We encourage you to carefully familiarize yourself with privacy policies applicable to any websites and/or services operated by third parties. Please be aware that we are not responsible for the privacy practices of any third parties.
Information We Collect
Information
We
Collect
from
You
Directly
When you interact with the Service, or any Mageeks’s Site or Game, we may collect and store information from you directly as described below. We collect information in the following circumstances: when you use our Games, when you visit our Site, when a User Account is created and managed, when you connect your User Account to your Facebook or other third-party account, when you participate in any interactive features of the Service, and when you otherwise communicate with us or via the Service.
The information you provide to us directly may include, without limitation, the following information that may, in certain circumstances, constitute personal data:
Data that you provide to us in connection with your User Account / profile, such as your age, gender and the country / city where you live in.
If you subscribe to our mailing list, we collect your email address and first name.
We collect data that you may share in the Service, such as postings in forums, chats, message boards and blogs, when you invite friends to use the Service, and other interactive features of the Service, your public profile, and your friends list in the Service;
Data that you may provide in connection with any promotions that may be an element of the Service;
Any other information you may want to share with us, such as personal data related to
recruitment / job applications.
We may allow you to connect your Mageeks User Account to your social media account(s). If you connect to your social mecha account(s) such as through Facebook Connect, Apple’s Game Center, Google Services, or any other third party service, we may collect personal data, such as your user ID, name, e-mail address, and profile picture that are available in your public profile with such third party. We may also collect other data such as posts, comments, media, and applications. You may be able to control the types of personal data available in the profile of such third party services by adjusting the privacy settings available therein. We may also show your name and profile picture within the Service.
If you connect your Mageeks’s User Account to your social media account, you may also use you log- in details across platforms and on different devices to identify yourself while using the Service.
Moreover, if you contact us, a record of this correspondence may be kept. Payment information related to transactions carried out in the Service is processed by a third party payment processor, such as Apple, Google, or Amazon.
Please note that any content posted to a forum or other interactive features in the Service will be visible and available to other users of the Service. We are not responsible for and do not guarantee the security of the information you choose to share in the Service. Please practice caution when sharing your personal data in the Service.
Data Collected Automatically
We collect statistical information on the device you use to access the Service. This device data may include, without limitation, device manufacturer and type, information about the operating system of your device, the name of your internet service provider, connection type, device language, unique device identifiers, iOS device name, Android ID, Advertising ID, screen size, processor cores, total disk space, remaining disk space, IDFA (unique identifier for iOS) and the Internet Protocol (IP) address from which you access the Service. We may also use device data to identify the device throughout different Games.
Technologies such as cookies, tags and scripts are used in the Service. We use technology
created by third parties to enable such technological features. We may also automatically collect the URL of the site from which you came and the site to which you are going when you leave the Service.
We use third party data analytics service providers. Analytics Service Providers collect and
store data such as time of visit, pages visited, time spent on each page of the Site, the Internet Protocol (IP) address, and the type of operating system used in the devices used to access the Service. The current list of data analytics service providers we use in connection with the Service is: Google Analytics, Firebase, Facebook Analytics, Kochava Analytics, Unity Analytics, Branch.
We collect information on your location based on your IP address. By using the Service, you
give your consent to the collection of location data.
When you use the Service, we automatically collect and store certain information regarding use
of the Service. We may track how our Games and the Service in general is used using your device. As you play our Games, we collect data about your interactions with the Game and with the other players in the Game, such as your in-game purchase history and game play history.
Moreover, details of your visits to the Service including, but not limited to, traffic data, weblogs and other communication data may also be collected.
How We Use Information
In general, We collect, store and use your information to provide you with a safe, smooth, efficient, and customized experience with the Service. For example, we may use information collected from you in the following ways:
create game account and allow you to play our games;
identify and suggest connections with other users;
operate and improve our Service;
understand you and your preferences to enhance your experience and enjoyment using our Service;
respond to your comments and questions and provide customer service;
provide and deliver products and services you request;
send you related information, including confirmations, invoices, technical notices, updates, security alerts, and support and administrative messages;
communicate with you about promotions, rewards, upcoming events, and other news about the
Service or Services of our selected partners;
enable you to communicate with other users;
prevent fraud or potentially illegal activities
deliver and target advertising
link or combine it with other information we get from third parties, to help understand your preferences and provide you with better services.
Ad Networks
We may feature advertising within our Service. The advertisers may collect and use information about you, such as your Service session activity, device identifier and IP address. They may use this information to provide advertisements of interest to you.
In addition, you may see our games advertised in other services. After clicking on one of these advertisements and installing our game, you will become a user of our Service. In order to verify the installs, a device identifier may be shared with the advertiser.
Opting Out of Marketing
You can stop all collection of information by Mageeks’s Games easily by uninstalling our Games. You may use the standard uninstall processes as may be available as part of your mobile device or via the mobile application marketplace or network.
When you install our Games on your mobile device you can choose to receive push notifications. You can turn off push notifications by visiting the “options” or “settings” page within the relevant Game. You may also receive local notifications. You can turn off local notifications by visiting the “options” or “settings” page within the relevant Game.
You may opt-out of receiving promotional emails from us by following the instructions in those emails. If you opt-out, we may still send you non-promotional emails, such as emails about your accounts or our ongoing business relations.
Disclosure of Your information
We may share your personal information with the following categories of third parties:
To service providers, such as data analysis companies
To our advertising partners
To public authorities, such as law enforcement, if we are legally required to do so or if we need to protect our rights or the rights of third parties
To our subsidiaries and affiliates; or a subsequent owner, co-owner or operator of the Service
and their advisors in connection with a corporate merger, consolidation, restructuring, the sale of substantially all of our stock and/or assets, or in connection with bankruptcy proceedings, or other corporate reorganization, in accordance with this Privacy Policy
We may also share aggregate or anonymous information about you with advertisers, publishers,
business partners, sponsors, and other third parties. This information does not constitute personal data as it doesn’t allow to identify you personally.
Your Rights
You have the right to know what data we hold about you, the right to update, correct or delete your data and the right to opt our of receiving marketing communication from us. If you would like to know what personal data we hold about you, would like to delete or update your personal data please contact us at
privacy@mageeks.com.
Security
We are concerned about safeguarding the confidentiality of your information. We provide physical, electronic, and procedural safeguards to protect information we process and maintain. For example, we limit access to this information to authorized employees and contractors who need to know that information in order to operate, develop or improve our Service. We do not warrant or represent that your information will be protected against, loss, misuse, or alteration by third parties. No method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure, however. Therefore, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
Our Policy Regarding Children
This Service is not directed to children younger than thirteen (13) years of age. We do not intend to collect personal data from children under 13. If you are under 13, please do not use the Service and do not send any information about yourself to us. In the event that we learn that we have collected personal information from a child under age 13, we will delete that information as quickly as possible.
International Transfer
Some elements of the Service may be hosted on servers located in countries outside your own country
and in particular outside the European Union. The laws applicable to the protection of personal data in such countries may be different from those applicable in your home country. By using the Service, you consent to personal data about you being transferred outside your own country. In particular, if you are located within the European Union, you consent to your personal data being transferred outside of the European Union.
Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy here. You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes.
Contact Us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Service, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at
privacy@mageeks.com.